title: Headlines from the Future
itunes:title: Headlines from the Future
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, & Gregg Rosenthal– recap all the latest news from around the NFL including DeShone Kizer starting for the Browns, Odell Beckham Jr’s hard hit, and Rex Ryan’s odds of returning to the NFL. The heroes present their Rotoworld blurbs from the future and dissect Trash Takes with Patrick Claybon.
